  ('https://www.vox.com/2019/5/29/18638924/giving-pledge-ben-delo-far-future','Britain’s youngest self-made billionaire is giving away his fortune — to people who don’t exist yet. The case for charity to benefit the far future.','2019-05-29',NULL,'Kelsey Piper','Vox','Ben Delo','Center for Human-Compatible AI|Forethought Foundation for Global Priorities Research','Broad donor strategy','Global catastrophic risks|Effective altruism','Kelsey Piper reports that Ben Delo, co-founder of cryptocurrency trading platform BitMEX, has signed the Giving Pledge, and will focus his giving on the long term. Piper includes arguments in favor of Delo''s choice of focus, and describes the role the effective altruism movement played in influencing him.');
